
                         Berkeley Packet Filter (BPF)
                         ----------------------------

1. Introduction
----------------

Enable BPF and related syscalls and JIT

If you need more details, Please see linux/Documnetation/networking/filter.txt

2. Usage
--------

Add this template using the following configure script option.
i.e.: --templates feature/bpf

This will ensure the required kernel config values are set. 
